## 4. Specific Sections of `interactive-mode.js` (4793 lines total)

### Lines 1-100: Imports & Top Comments
```js
/**
 * Interactive mode for the coding agent.
 * Handles TUI rendering and user interaction, delegating business logic to AgentSession.
 */
```

The single line comment on line 1 says "delegating business logic to AgentSession" вҖ” this is the **only** mention of any delegation pattern. It refers to delegating to AgentSession (the runtime), not to sub-agents.

### Lines 150-170: workingVisible / workingMessage Config
