**Root cause found.** Render batching.

```js
// tui.js:459-473
requestRender(force = false) {
    if (this.renderRequested) return;  // вҶҗ DROPS duplicate requests
    this.renderRequested = true;
    process.nextTick(() => this.scheduleRender());
}

scheduleRender() {
    const delay = Math.max(0, MIN_RENDER_INTERVAL_MS - elapsed);
    this.renderTimer = setTimeout(() => {  // вҶҗ DEFERRED
        this.doRender();
    }, delay);
}
```

`requestRender()` deduplicates. If 50 `tool_execution_update` events fire before the next render tick, only the LAST state renders. By then, `tool_execution_end` has already fired and replaced the partial result with `вң“ scout (33 turns)`.

